Author: Harman Preet
Body: Really useful. With outstanding features, Binance is the Best of the Best CryptoCurrency Exchange in the market. The app contains over 80 cryptocurrency pairs and is user-friendly. It also has a cryptocurrency of its own, called BNB. Etc What more could a cryptocurrency exchange possibly provide? I adore this exchange platform always. The portal and integrated crypto exchange have excellent design. This is one of my favourite cryptocurrency exchanges, and I can assure you this is best for you.

Author: Shannon Whitford
Body: This app loves to take your money, but loves to lock you out and slow you down if you ever want to take your money out, went ages unable to get in, and now the convert button is randonly gone when I need it. Possibly user error, but the whole thing feels shady as hell. Might be better using a browser, but this app is mostly just annoying.
